org.pimslims.business.core.service
Interface ConstructService

All Superinterfaces:
BaseService, PropertyNameConvertor<ConstructView>, ViewService<ConstructView>
public interface ConstructService
    
extends BaseService, ViewService<ConstructView>



This Service will get the information about the construct used in an
experiment. Since this information is held and managed by Core PIMS, this should
really just be a link to how to access this information in the Core PIMS GUI -
we do not want to have to reinvent the wheel to view these things!
